      "properties": {
        "Node name for S&R": "Note"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "ATLAS INPUT QUICKSTART \u2014 image in, projected relief out.\n\nDefaults = instant relief: one high-res mesh, first queue in seconds. Then grow into the master workflow's behaviors without leaving this node:\n\n\u00b7 layers 2\u20134 \u2014 depth-band clean-plate layers (watertight splits)\n\u00b7 use_vlm \u2014 the \ud83e\udded assessment configures prompts/geometry/bands per image (forces 4 bands)\n\u00b7 sky + sky_prompt \u2014 SAM sky card (needs ComfyUI-RMBG)\n\u00b7 scope_prompts \u2014 one SAM prompt per band, far\u2192near; self-disarming on no-match\n\u00b7 inpaint (+ upscale_model) \u2014 per-band LaMa clean plates (needs comfyui-inpaint-nodes + big-lama.pt)\n\nMissing packs never error \u2014 features skip and the report output says so. When you outgrow this node: examples/atlas_camera_staged_master_workflow.json is the same logic with stages, gates and per-layer debug."
      ]
    },
